reviewText: I had been dying to watch Snoopy Come Home this past summer and decided it was time to add it to my collection. I first found this double feature, which I had no clue existed but was so thrilled because A Boy Named Charlie Brown is just as fantastic as Snoopy Come Home, at a local electronics store for $34 and was reluctant to buy at that price. Luckily I had my trusty Amazon iPhone App and I quickly found the same product for less than half the price! The shipping was as fast as always. I am so pleased with this product!
Title: Peanuts Double Feature: Snoopy Come Home and A Boy Named Charlie Brown

reviewText: The grandkids love all the peanut characters. These DVD came with a great price because you have two for the reasonable price almost for one.Love it.

reviewText: I really love the Peanuts Gang, especially Charlie Brown and Snoopy! I grew up watching these movies! Every since I was a kid I always wanted to watch their shows every time I turn on the T.V. I really enjoy the movie "A boy name Charlie Brown!" And you gotta love the movie "Snoopy Come Home!" This is the best DVD I ever order! Thanks Amazon!Dee SmallsDecatur GA!
summary: These movies are the best! Talk about 2 in 1!
